!!CAUTION!!
Do not execute this test on a device without manual control.
The test will render the device unbootable and disable adb.
Manual control is required to return the device to fastboot.

To run the tests:

$ export ANDROID_SERIAL=[adb device id]
$ phablet-config writable-image

$ adt-run --no-built-binaries --unbuilt-tree bootfail -o log-dir --- \
      ssh -s /usr/share/autopkgtest/ssh-setup/adb -- -s $ANDROID_SERIAL

Exit code is '0' if it passed.
Logs are stored under log-dir as specified with the '-o' option.
